Name: Avik Tripura Pathao Inc
Review Text: So the reason for this one star review is basically cause I got scammed by one your riders and I later realized there is so complaint system in your whole platform. Not in your website or in your app. This is a greatly overlooked design issue. Please look into this. Anyway for my complaint, Id like ...Full ReviewSo the reason for this one star review is basically cause I got scammed by one your riders and I later realized there is so complaint system in your whole platform. Not in your website or in your app. This is a greatly overlooked design issue. Please look into this. Anyway for my complaint, Id like to say that I choose my destination and called the rider. Usually all the riders call but this one did not so I just waited a while and called him. The ride itself was alright and he seemed to be a reasonable is server. However when it came to the payment, he said my ride cost 203 taka. I knew this was not possible cause a) I applied is the discount and I was well bellow that and b) even if it was higher it wouldn't reach that high. He did not show me the cost as he hid the actual number using his hands. I paid him anyway seeing I got to my destination safe and sound but I feel like I got cheated. More so that the rider did not appear in my history. Which leads me to believe that he did not register the ride for that trip. This made me upset and I tried to actually reach pathao to complain but you have no outlets for said complaint. Everything is convergent in terms of feed back. How are you going to improve the service if it does not let users voice their opinions? This was not a technical issue (but there are those such as frequent crashes and the GPS bug which doesn't go away if you don't restart the whole app), but I feel like these are the problems you should look to address. Anyway I just wanted to write this for your own company benefit and hope you fix this. Till I get a remedy or a reply I will use alternative services like uber or shohoj. If you made it this far, thank you for reading and more importantly, may you take some actions. Edit: Well damn, and now you people are accused of stealing user data and your excuse is "women security". Jeez. . . I was hoping to recorrect my review but I never got the call back for a follow up in the email. Anyway too late. I know you will not be affected by the current fiasco much but please do take user feed back into consideration. Today was the last day for a happy hour for a certain restaurant and the menu doesn't show up in you app. Just Heads up. You have permanently lost an user.

Name: AH SHUVO Pathao Inc
Review Text: অাপনারা টাকার লোভে যারে তারে Rider List এ যোগ করছেন। যেসকল রিকসাওয়ালা বাইক চালানো শিখেনাই তাদের পর্যন্ত Add করে নিচ্ছেন। অাপনাদের চেয়ে অন্যান্য রাইড শেয়ারিং এ্যাপস অনেক ভাল কারণ তারা যারে তারে যোগ কইরা নেয়না। এভাবে বেশিদিন টিকে থাকতে পারবেন না। অাপনাদের রাইডার রা কতটা Unprofessional অার খারাপ সেটা স...Full Reviewঅাপনারা টাকার লোভে যারে তারে Rider List এ যোগ করছেন। যেসকল রিকসাওয়ালা বাইক চালানো শিখেনাই তাদের পর্যন্ত Add করে নিচ্ছেন। অাপনাদের চেয়ে অন্যান্য রাইড শেয়ারিং এ্যাপস অনেক ভাল কারণ তারা যারে তারে যোগ কইরা নেয়না। এভাবে বেশিদিন টিকে থাকতে পারবেন না। অাপনাদের রাইডার রা কতটা Unprofessional অার খারাপ সেটা সবাই জানে এখন। একমাত্র অাপনাদের এড করা অশিক্ষিত মুর্খ সিএনজিওয়ালা টাইপ রাইডার রাই হবে অাপনাদের পতনের কারণ। পারলে নতুন নিয়ম চালু করুন। শুধুমাত্র শিক্ষিত দেরকে Add করুন অাপনাদের রাইডার লিস্টে। বিশেষ করে যাদের যোগ্যতা নুন্যতম H.S.C Pass তাদেরকে Add করুন অার বাকি অশিক্ষিতদেরকে ছাটাই করুন। রাইড শেয়ারিং মাধ্যমে অশিক্ষিতরা থেকে গেলে অাপনাদের পতন হতে বেশি সময় লাগবেনা। জানি কথাগুলো অাপনারা কানে নিবেন না এখন। কিন্তু একদিন ঠিকই বুঝতে পারবেন যখন সকল ইউজার হারাবেন। অলরেডি সবাই অাপনাদেরকে বয়কট করা শুরু করেছে। অাপনাদের অশিক্ষিত মুর্খ রাইডারদের কাছে কেউ Safe না।

Review Text: It's ok, but there are times when it shows longer route for short route. Recently can't see cars around. Furthermore now it's more complicated like car plus just cars simple. Time taken search especially on mobile data is longer and real time travel data is slow too. No option to pay driver directly...Full ReviewIt's ok, but there are times when it shows longer route for short route. Recently can't see cars around. Furthermore now it's more complicated like car plus just cars simple. Time taken search especially on mobile data is longer and real time travel data is slow too. No option to pay driver directly by bkash or other common mobile wallet. Fix these and I think it'll be the quickest way to call a ride system.

Shame on you.

Al...Full ReviewThe app has gone haywire recently. Too needy and desperate for everyone to use their saturated services. For devices with 18:9 aspect ratio (i.e, oneplus 6), whenever i try to select a destination, the inbox messages pop up and therefore i cant see what i am ...Full ReviewPathao just made my life whole lot easier. But some things must be addressed. I hope that the devs would see and reply to this comment.        1. For devices with 18:9 aspect ratio (i.e, oneplus 6), whenever i try to select a destination, the inbox messages pop up and therefore i cant see what i am typing or what my search result suggestions are. If i lower the inbox messages then the keyboard also goes down. This is a huge bummer because the destination searching becomes very troublesome. This is my number one issue with the software.       2. Again for devices with 18:9 aspect ratio (i.e, oneplus 6), when the fair shows, half of that is covered by the search rider button. So the final fair needs to be assumed because of this issue.               3. Sometimes the fair increases by a lot because of high demand. This practice should be stopped as it is unfair to charge extra than the regulation and calculations pathao promised us regarding fair values.  Kudos for pathao pay though. It just made the "battle for change"  totally null and void.

EXTRA HELMET?

Name: Yusuf Rashid
Review Text: It's time to either they provide helmet to every passenger or boycott them. After every completion of the journey, driver review automatic comes to the app screen, after the review they ask, do the driver provided a helmet or not? Obviously, as I use Pathao many many times, and never offered a helme...Full ReviewIt's time to either they provide helmet to every passenger or boycott them. After every completion of the journey, driver review automatic comes to the app screen, after the review they ask, do the driver provided a helmet or not? Obviously, as I use Pathao many many times, and never offered a helmet by any driver, NO. But what is use for this review? If you don't care the Yes or No options clicked by the passenger, if you don't care your rider provide a helmet to the passengers or not, so it's the time to boycott Pathao now. The day before yesterday a passenger died by an accident in the Airport road, the killer bus (sorry to say) broke his head by the front wheel, led to an instant death. If he would have worn a helmet, may be, 1% chance, may be he would have not killed, rather injured or lived. Not only this accident, many other accident happen other days. You must provide a helmet before a ride to every passenger. Though our country's law & order is never obedient, and that's why we all are used to denying the least formalities.

to go with this particular driver. Needs to have detailed rating system. A ...Full ReviewThe app needs to have an option to manually input your location because 
sometimes location service on your phone might not work properly. Doesn't 
show driver profile. Driver profile gives a choice to the rider if he wants 
to go with this particular driver. Needs to have detailed rating system. A 
lot of drivers cancel after accepting the request saying they won't go to 
the rider's destination. This issue needs to be solved. For basic 
ride-sharing functionality, this app is OK but can do so much better if 
certain issues are handled better.

Name: Mushfiqur Rahman
Review Text: The app is good but has some major problems: 1. The location often states wrong address after placing the pin correctly on the map 2. Often the app hangs or is very slow when loading, especially when calling a ride or closing a ride. 3. The estimated fare is often wrong. I have seen the map taking i...Full ReviewThe app is good but has some major problems: 1. The location often states wrong address after placing the pin correctly on the map 2. Often the app hangs or is very slow when loading, especially when calling a ride or closing a ride. 3. The estimated fare is often wrong. I have seen the map taking into account lots of extra unncessary roads which adds to the actual cost, instead of taking the shortest route.  My advice: Please follow the Uber app, it is very well designed. A good service with a bad app won't get you customer satisfaction.

Name: Tanvir Hasib
Review Text: The company have increased the fare without informing the customers. Now I'm paying 15-20 taka more than I used to pay 1 / 2 weeks back. They have increase the rate and on the other hand giving discounts on the rate. So ultimately it is remaining all most the same. These companies will never change ...Full ReviewThe company have increased the fare without informing the customers. Now I'm paying 15-20 taka more than I used to pay 1 / 2 weeks back. They have increase the rate and on the other hand giving discounts on the rate. So ultimately it is remaining all most the same. These companies will never change their psychology. When they grow popularity, they become like Hyena. Gulshan 2 to Lalmatia is now BDT 165 to BDT 170 in Pathao whereas now a days CNGs are charging BDT 200 for the same destination. So if I don't have any urgency (which is most of the time), I would rather choose CNGs as my transport. I'm sure there will be more passengers thinking like me. Moreover no Pathao drivers offer helmet for their passengers.
